Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}被囚禁 的 学园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此再次宣布 成立日本合众国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这一瞬间开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间就是日本合众国第一块领土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不问人种 主义 宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为国民的资格只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是行使正义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来取ZERO的性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是电话 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直联络不到你 担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 在安全的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在演说的ZERO 是别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 我才要问你现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维蕾塔老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修已经回学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要补习了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早点回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话打完了？孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是完了 各种意义上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团残党与自称ZERO的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在仍据守在中华联邦总领事馆中的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德代理总督已代替负伤的卡拉雷斯总督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率军将领事馆重重包围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此可以说租界安全已得到保证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的骚动啊 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己领土之中突然建了个国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个国家还向自己宣战了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几时替换的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演说前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音是录音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现的时候就已经换人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟魔术表演一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人不爽 连我们都瞒着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我们」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「我」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 开炉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放盐
