Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白奶油酱（Bechamel Sauce）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利冰淇淋（Gelato）另盛一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷迭香（Rosemary）拿出来放冰沙（Sorbet）里
