Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑森林蛋糕（Schwarzwalder Kirschtorte）…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不定啦 那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我这么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊 利瓦尔是味痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不擅长细致活是吧 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么老实多好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种角色本该没生活能力才正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还写家计簿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要毛巾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 能问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能答不上来 不过你问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 是我和罗洛的生还纪念派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 亏你们能从恐怖袭击中生还
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉可担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「要是鲁鲁死了 那我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 罗洛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是有叫他来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道他跟哥哥不同 比较纯朴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样才交不到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫做文静啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 沾到身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都弄得粘糊糊的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不记得娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是妹妹被假弟弟替换了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅篡改了我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把学生会的所有人都当成玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴别塔事件以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修·兰佩洛奇并未显示出特别的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校内有180个隐藏摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便衣的监视人员也有47名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视人员是48名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也没有情报显示卡尔塔哥队的全灭与鲁路修有关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有使用Geass的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若他是ZERO 再潜回学校也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 C.C.到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若未和鲁路修接触
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在总领事馆的可能性也很低
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 和事件前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行踪不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们机密情报局将继续执行C.C.捕获作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各员 和以往一样继续监视诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方中枢是监视数据的接收方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺去大家有关娜娜莉的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为知道娜娜莉不会出现在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 布里塔尼亚皇帝很可能掌握着娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是连亲生儿女都会当工具利用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若知道我的记忆…知道我已恢复ZERO的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能鲁莽行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要欺瞒 骗过监视我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的课也要乖乖去上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就那么没信用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维蕾塔·纽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾中过我Geass的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Geass对一个人只能用一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 Geass对她已没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就从本不该存在的弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先从这家伙开始温柔地攻略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左翼德意志州军开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荷兰工兵 制压地雷区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右翼的意大利州军也撑住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今晚的波尔多（Bordeaux）将是胜利的美酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正上方出现未确认机体1架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的白色死神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆桌骑士来前线了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器的人 本人不会攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打下来 敌人只有一架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 单独作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木本来就是殿下的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是第七骑士（Knight of Seven）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下的直属部下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该为他的荣升感到高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界现在还充满悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他有身为路标的自觉和责任感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟被朱雀带走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想起看相册？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是学生会马拉松舞会的文档吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长太热衷搞活动也真让人头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失恋比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催人泪下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是会长把奖杯交给优胜的利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你能逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻播了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴别塔被军方完全包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是怎么突破包围圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是「怎样从恐怖分子手中逃出来的」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有紧急通道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想通知你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那种情况下手机不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了 那挂坠盒是我给他的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 10月25日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是娜娜莉的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 那个挂坠盒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想 给男生挂坠盒有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该给你别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这是你给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 鲁路修的监视情况无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全无使用过Geass的形迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚Geass的详情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教团的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在谈话吗 我稍后再来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是执行同一任务的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的指使…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能被听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京管区也是只有我们才知道的机密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你这样杀了多少队员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最确实迅速的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本合众国成立后已过了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚不可能这样一直僵持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦本国 也有总领事更替的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还没收到鲁路修的下一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已推迟了布里塔尼亚发来的引渡交涉要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计能撑一周
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会转告ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是中华联邦政府的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想来 你扮兔女郎不是更直截了当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是…女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也暴露得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没幽默感的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拿ZERO当游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸会 红月卡莲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是红莲二式的机师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 扇先生他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到吗 ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是科奈莉娅·R·布里塔尼亚公主的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔伯特·G·P·吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天15时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将对犯下叛国罪的特一级罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,256人进行处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你珍惜部下的的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和我堂堂正正决一胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德 真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 就鲁鲁一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是夏莉你 游泳部怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被抓来负责买生日礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顾问维蕾塔老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家说我也老惹她生气 正好做个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不擅长选礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是买酒吧 看她好像喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是品种什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你去选礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢提供素材
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能抑制你那失控的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若只是屏蔽光信息就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那普通的彩色隐形眼镜也行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别试探我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所知 这是特制的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 若你的Geass变得比现在更强…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前我会做个了结的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去帮忙选礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维蕾塔老师要过生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 生日是很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗～洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 你也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是交流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,475)}嗯 我也只是知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,475)}没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,475)}那边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,475)}贵腐酒可能太甜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是选索普隆红酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就当是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过竟连罗洛也拖来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真像会长的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来能成为男女交流生态学会演讲的好材料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此就拖人家来跟踪哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛也有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会成为亲人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对象通过预测路线Z（Zebra）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 和7班交换
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2班进行警戒准备与C.C.接触
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始周边清理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地在巴别塔设下了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 敌人不是租界的总督府
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽不知道谁是监视者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但系统本身有漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会对明天部下的处刑坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆还是没有恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 这里该怎么写
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 能劳驾一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想坐一次缆车来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我夏莉才会失去记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还擅自篡改了会长和利瓦尔的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一切结束之后 一定让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长他们跟着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标即将进店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α14 是间小店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若跟进店可能会被察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在店前待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3人绕去后门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你暂时在这儿等着 假装我在里面好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我悄悄出店 吓会长他们一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时我不会来这种店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该不会有监视器或窃听器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉以为只是无谓的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一失败 也不会连累她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass的设置也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 表参道Mall警备室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不按以下要求行事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就引爆预设在你们那里的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 他不可能是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,函馆租界来的马克西米利安先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,函馆租界来的马克西米利安先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖袭击的警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO都复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小声点 会被客人们发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表参道Mall接到黑色骑士团的爆炸通牒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配置不变 准备与C.C.接触
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,条件已成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差按下起爆按钮
