Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖袭击？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走散啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scorpion（罗洛的代号）的报告怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为维持治安 手机信号受到临时干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校 Scorpion的报告不是最优先的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去现场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓恐慌 就是这样制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的位置在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都去找C.C.了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然…觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟踪者已成为我的奴隶 绝对服从于我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们果然将捕捉C.C.视为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使情报错误
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这鸟笼般的学园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此刻起就是我自由的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你 将成为寻找娜娜莉的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止了时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 你就与那恶魔之瞳一同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团 就在此毁灭吧
